OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1782296300
OL,3,CBurst water main leaves homes in
OL,4,CWitney without tap water or low
OL,5,Cpressure
OL,7,FPeople in Witney in Oxfordshire are
OL,8,Fwithout water or low pressure because
OL,9,Fof a burst water main.
OL,11,FThames Water confirmed they have a
OL,12,Fteam on site at Poffley End trying to
OL,13,Ffix the problem.
OL,15,FA spokesperson said: "We're sorry if
OL,16,Fyour tap water isn't running at the
OL,17,Fmoment.
OL,19,F"We're aware of an issue affecting
OL,20,Fcustomers in Witney, OX29 area.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
