PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1782296300
OL,3,CBurst water main leaves homes in
OL,4,CWitney without tap water or low
OL,5,Cpressure
OL,7,F"Our specialist team is on site at
OL,8,FPoffley End to restore the flow of
OL,9,Fyour water supply.
OL,11,F"We're currently working to isolate
OL,12,Fthis burst pipe and will be able to
OL,13,Fbegin repairs shortly after.
OL,15,F"We know how disruptive it is if you
OL,16,Flose your water supply, so we'll work
OL,17,Fhard to get things back to normal as
OL,18,Fsoon as we can.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
