OL,3,CBurst water main leaves homes in
OL,4,CWitney without tap water or low
OL,5,Cpressure
OL,7,F"If you or someone you know needs a
OL,8,Flittle extra support, our free
OL,9,FPriority Services Register can help us
OL,10,Fto understand your situation so we can
OL,11,Ftake it into account as best we can."
OL,13,FWest Oxfordshire District Council is
OL,14,Furging people to check on their
OL,15,Fvulnerable neighbours who may not have
OL,16,Fwater.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
