OL,3,CBurst water main leaves homes in
OL,4,CWitney without tap water or low
OL,5,Cpressure
OL,7,FA council spokesperson said: "With hot
OL,8,Fweather continuing across the
OL,9,Fdistrict, please check in on
OL,10,Fvulnerable neighbours, friends and
OL,11,Frelatives, particularly if they are
OL,12,Fwithout water."
